{
  "text": "Human platelets were isolated as described previously. [CITATION_1] Human arterial endothelial cells (HAECs) were isolated and passaged according to techniques described previously. [CITATION_2] Human CD34 \u03e9 cells were isolated either from human cord blood or from bone marrow and cultured as described previously. 18",
